---
// src/pages/contact.astro
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>お問い合わせ | AIとの付き合い方研究所</title>
  <meta name="description" content="AIとの付き合い方研究所へのお問い合わせはこちらから。記事の感想・ご意見・取材依頼など、お気軽にどうぞ。" />

  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@700;800&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;500;600&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500&display=swap');

    :root {
      --ink: #111111;
      --ink-soft: #2b2b2b;
      --ink-muted: #666666;

      --paper: #f7f4ee;
      --paper-card: #fcfaf6;

      --amber: #c87c22;
      --amber-light: rgba(200,124,34,.08);
      --amber-line: rgba(200,124,34,.35);

      --border: rgba(0,0,0,.10);
      --border-mid: rgba(0,0,0,.18);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--paper);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* HEADER */

    .site-header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(247,244,238,.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .site-header-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .site-logo {
      font-family: "Noto Serif JP", serif;
      font-size: .85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      letter-spacing: .06em;
    }

    .site-logo span {
      color: var(--amber);
    }

    .back-link {
      font-size: .8rem;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      transition: color .15s;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
      color: var(--amber);
    }

    /* PAGE WRAP */

    .page-wrap {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem 6rem;
    }

    /* PAGE HEADER */

    .page-header {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .page-eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      font-family: "Syne", sans-serif;
      font-size: .65rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .2em;
      color: var(--amber);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      padding-bottom: .5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--amber-line);
    }

    .page-title {
      font-family: "Noto Serif JP", serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .page-desc {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 2.1;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
    }

    /* CONTACT TYPES */

    .contact-types {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .contact-type {
      background: var(--paper-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 1.2rem 1.3rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: .4rem;
    }

    .contact-type-label {
      font-size: .65rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      color: var(--amber);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .contact-type-text {
      font-size: .85rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
    }

    /* FORM SECTION HEAD */

    .form-section-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
      padding-bottom: 1.2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      position: relative;
    }

    .form-section-head::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -1px;
      left: 0;
      width: 60px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--amber);
    }

    .form-section-title {
      font-family: "Noto Serif JP", serif;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    /* FORM BUTTON CARD */

    .form-button-wrap {
      background: var(--paper-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .form-button-text {
      font-size: .92rem;
      line-height: 2;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
    }

    .form-button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .5rem;
      font-family: "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
      font-size: .88rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
      background: var(--amber);
      padding: .85rem 1.7rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: opacity .2s;
    }

    .form-button:hover {
      opacity: .85;
    }

    .form-button::after {
      content: "→";
    }

    /* NOTE */

    .form-note {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
      background: var(--amber-light);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--amber);
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .form-note p {
      font-size: .82rem;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
    }

    /* FOOTER */

    .site-footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .site-footer-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .footer-brand {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: .6rem;
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-family: "Noto Serif JP", serif;
      font-size: .9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
    }

    .footer-logo span {
      color: var(--amber);
    }

    .footer-copy {
      font-size: .72rem;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .footer-link {
      font-size: .8rem;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      transition: color .15s;
    }

    .footer-link:hover {
      color: var(--amber);
    }

    /* RESPONSIVE */

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .page-wrap {
        padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 5rem;
      }

      .contact-types {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .page-title {
        font-size: 1.65rem;
      }

      .form-button-wrap {
        padding: 1.8rem 1.4rem;
      }

      .form-button {
        align-self: stretch;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .site-footer-inner {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }

      .footer-links {
        gap: 1.2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="site-header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="site-logo">
        AI<span>との付き合い方</span>研究所
      </a>
      <a href="/" class="back-link">← 記事一覧</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="page-wrap">

      <header class="page-header">
        <span class="page-eyebrow">Contact</span>
        <h1 class="page-title">お問い合わせ</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">
          記事への感想・ご意見、取材・執筆のご依頼、その他ご質問など、<br>
          お気軽にご連絡ください。
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="contact-types">
        <div class="contact-type">
          <span class="contact-type-label">感想・意見</span>
          <p class="contact-type-text">記事を読んで感じたこと、気になった点など</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-type">
          <span class="contact-type-label">取材・依頼</span>
          <p class="contact-type-text">執筆・登壇・メディア掲載などのご相談</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-type">
          <span class="contact-type-label">その他</span>
          <p class="contact-type-text">上記に当てはまらないご質問・ご要望</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-section-head">
        <h2 class="form-section-title">フォームから送る</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="form-button-wrap">
        <p class="form-button-text">
          Googleフォームが別タブで開きます。<br>
          必要事項をご記入のうえ、送信してください。
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://forms.gle/A66jEkEvhhuu9eVs6"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="form-button"
        >
          お問い合わせフォームを開く
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="form-note">
        <p>
          いただいたお問い合わせには、内容を確認のうえ順次ご返信いたします。
          返信にはお時間をいただく場合がございます。あらかじめご了承ください。
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="site-footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <p class="footer-logo">AI<span>との付き合い方</span>研究所</p>
        <p class="footer-copy">
          ChatGPT・Claude・Geminiとの対話から、<br>
          AIと人間の関係を考えるブログ。
        </p>
      </div>
      <nav class="footer-links">
        <a href="/about" class="footer-link">このサイトについて</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="footer-link">プライバシーポリシー</a>
        <a href="/" class="footer-link">記事一覧へ戻る</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>